div.span: Please let us know if you buy something for Childs.

br.span: If you buy one of these items somewhere other than Amazon, please come back to Childs' list and click the "Buying this gift elsewhere?" link next to the item you purchased and follow the instructions to reserve the item. This will help ensure Childs does not get duplicate gifts.

td.span: All items purchased from this list will go directly to the Children's​ Hospital at Georgia Health Sciences Children's Medical Center in Augusta, GA. This charity's tax ID # is 35-2310573​. PLEASE NOTE: All items must be new and unwrapped.​ Please do not purchase used items or have them giftwrappe​d. Thank you!
